	ns4:sourceId	"1AeGZbVGklg23tg" ;
	ns2:description	"Level 5 has a steep gradient and may not be suitable for sufferers of vertigo. Bag Policy No briefcases, bags, luggage or large purses as Wembley Stadium operates a restricted bag policy. Each person can only bring one small bag in to the stadium, and it must not be bigger than A4 size: - Height - 297mm (11.7 inches) - Width - 210mm (8.27 inches) - Depth - 210mm (8.27 inches) Bags that are half-full and folded over to reduce their size will not be accepted. Anyone carrying bags that do not meet the criteria above will not be allowed in to the stadium." ;
