ns3:G5dzZbzTYk4gI	rdf:type	ns2:Event ;
	ns4:sourceId	"G5dzZbzTYk4gI" ;
	ns2:description	"Security - Bag Policy: Large bags including rucksacks are not allowed. There are no facilities to leave large bags or luggage. If you really have to bring a bag - and it's preferable you don't, please make sure it's small. Only one small bag per person is permitted and it must not be bigger than A4 size. Height: 28.7cm Width: 21cm Depth 15cm" ;
