ns7:KovZ91777af	rdf:type	ns2:Place ;
	ns4:accessibilityNote	"To book accessible tickets, check here on Ticketmaster of email the access team at access@o2academybrixton.co.uk O2 Academy Brixton offers one companion ticket, free of charge to provide the support needed and additional assistance during the course of an emergency evacuation and so you know, proof of eligibility will be required. Companion tickets should be processed at the time of booking, by selecting one full price ticket, and one essential companion ticket, in the designated Accessible Ambulant or Accessible Wheelchair sections. Wheelchair spaces are available when you book, they are limited on a first come, first served basis. An accessible viewing platform is available in the stalls area There are a limited number of spaces for customers without our Circle seated area, including aisle and front rows, with options for you and your companion. Please contact us by email for more information. Note there are up to 50 (approx) steps to the Circle, we do not have lift access or an accessible toilet at this level." ;
	ns4:hasAccessibleSeating	"true"^^xsd:boolean ;
	ns4:sourceId	"KovZ91777af" ;
	ns2:address	ns51:address ;
	ns2:geo	ns51:geo ;
	ns2:url	<https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/o2-academy-brixton-tickets-london/venue/507981> ;
	ns2:name	"O2 Academy Brixton" .
<https://planorama.example.org/resource/event/17u8v0G65wW8Egc>	rdf:type	ns2:Event ;
	ns4:sourceId	"17u8v0G65wW8Egc" ;
	ns2:description	"Floor: Over 16s only. Under 15s must be accompanied by an adult over 18. A max of 4 tickets per person and per household applies. Tickets in excess of 4 will be cancelled. Kehlani has partnered with PLUS1 so that \u00A31 per ticket will be contributed towards The Kehlani Fund by Live Nation. https://www.plus1.org/ Seats located on Level 4 (Upper Tier, Upper Bowl) are not recommended for those who have a fear of heights. **Floor Seating is not raked and other customers might stand during the performance** **Letters of authorisation will not be accepted at the venue when collecting tickets for events at the O2. If collecting from the box office, the card holder must be present**" ;
	ns2:image	<https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/a/5e1/bef571fc-a24d-477f-9858-a7cc7d0055e1_TABLET_LANDSCAPE_LARGE_16_9.jpg> ;
