	ns4:sourceId	"1agZk3F0kPvZeC2" ;
	ns2:description	"Ages Seated: Over 16s only on the floor, Under 15s must be accompanied by an adult aged over 18. Ages Standing: Over 16s only. No under 16s permitted. A max of 4 tickets per person and per household applies. Tickets in excess of this will be cancelled. PLEASE NOTE seats located on Level 4 (Upper Tier, Upper Bowl) are not recommended for those who have a fear of heights. **Letters of authorisation will not be accepted at the venue when collecting tickets for events at the O2. If collecting from the box office, the card holder must be present**" ;
