<https://planorama.example.org/resource/event/1AdfZbMGkwFaV8n>	rdf:type	ns2:Event ;
	ns4:sourceId	"1AdfZbMGkwFaV8n" ;
	ns2:description	"Your \u00A31 will be donated to the newly launched Live Trust, a new funding initiative from LIVE that will offer much needed financial support to those working across live music. The Live Trust will initially support the grassroots music sector that is such a vital part of the music ecosystem - from venues and artists to festivals and promoters. Registered Charity Number 1211251 Evanescence has partnered with PLUS1. The proceeds raised from this fee of \u00A31.20 will go to support organizations providing humanitarian aid and medical relief to those in need around the world. Charity Registration Number: 46-4556468." ;
