	ns4:sourceId	"17u8v0G653a7sJE" ;
	ns2:description	"1.00* from every ticket sold on the tour will be donated to the newly launched Live Trust, a new funding initiative from LIVE that will offer much needed financial support to those working across live music. The Live Trust will initially support the grassroots music sector that is such a vital part of the music ecosystem - from venues and artists to festivals and promoters. * subject to taxes" ;
