	ns2:description	"American Express presents BST Hyde Park is delighted to announce a PDC darts Pro-Am tournament featuring top players Luke Humphries, Fallon Sherrock, Nathan Aspinall and Stephen Bunting in front of thousands of fans. PDC Presents The Hyde Park Darts Championship will take place on Wednesday 8th July, featuring special guests AJ Odudu, Behzinga, Emma Paton and the reigning champion Joe Swash. Tickets go on sale at 12pm on Thursday 28th May. The Hyde Park Darts Championship, featuring the sport?s top players, will be played out on BST Hyde Park?s famous Great Oak Stage." ;
