ns3:G5dzZ_uB_aV3U	rdf:type	ns2:Event ;
	ns4:sourceId	"G5dzZ_uB_aV3U" ;
	ns2:description	"This will be a Saturday night to remember: the Quarter Final. One win from the semis, one step closer to bringing it home. With DJs blasting iconic England anthems, the show starts long before kick-off. Expect the biggest atmosphere of the tournament so far. And the risk is on us, not you. If England don?t make it through to the QF, you'll get your money back. No excuses, no small print. Book with total confidence. The NEXT best place to watch the game, after the stadium It's us against the world WHAT TO EXPECT Show with England Legend | Thousands of England Fans! | Biggest Screens in UK | Stadium-like Atmosphere | Special Effects | Iconic Venue | Sky Sports Presenters | Live DJs & Music | Mouthwatering Food & Drink VIP Circle Row A & VIP Booth tickets include exclusive access to the VIP Bar. All seated tickets are general admission, first come first served." ;
	ns2:image	<https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/e/df2/e02dd07a-8e62-407a-84ed-739ddf40edf2_TABLET_LANDSCAPE_16_9.jpg> ;
