<https://planorama.example.org/resource/event/17u8v0G6uLNugEE>	rdf:type	ns2:Event ;
	ns4:sourceId	"17u8v0G6uLNugEE" ;
	ns2:description	"Experience Tennis Unrivaled when the ninth edition of the Laver Cup returns to The O2 in London from September 25-27, 2026. Born out of Roger Federer's idea to create an event to honor Australian tennis legend Rod Laver, the Laver Cup pits six of the best men's tennis players from Europe against six of their counterparts from the rest of the world over three days of intense team competition. The teams are led by legendary captains, Yannick Noah for Team Europe and Andre Agassi for Team World. Players confirmed to date: Team Europe: Carlos Alcaraz Alexander Zverev Flavio Cobolli Jakum Mensik Team World: Ben Shelton Alex de Minaur Taylor Fritz Alexander Bublik Additional players per team still to be announced. Played on a dramatic black court, the Laver Cup has superstar players as you have never seen them before...where rivals become teammates, competing in singles, teaming up in first-time doubles combinations, and cheering each other on from the sidelines." ;
	ns2:image	<https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/a/2a8/ed69abdb-5e83-4a6e-96f4-4f3b1670d2a8_TABLET_LANDSCAPE_16_9.jpg> ;
	ns2:startDate	"2026-09-25T16:30:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ;
	ns2:url	<https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/laver-cup-session-two-london-25-09-2026/event/350064D7E33759E7> ;
	ns4:hasCategory	ns6:sports-tennis-tennis ;
	ns2:name	"Laver Cup - Session Two" ;
	ns2:location	ns7:KovZ9177PFf ;
	ns2:performer	"Laver Cup" ;
	ns2:organizer	"ANSCO ARENA LIMITED" .
