<https://planorama.example.org/resource/event/17FYv0G65CJ9sfJ>	rdf:type	ns2:Event ;
	ns4:sourceId	"17FYv0G65CJ9sfJ" ;
	ns2:description	"No under 2s are permitted inside the stadium. Under 14s must be accompanied by an adult (18+). Juniors are allowed in all areas but in Licensed Standing they must be aged 12 and above. No under 12s are permitted in those areas. Bag Policy No briefcases, bags, luggage or large purses as Wembley Stadium operates a restricted bag policy. Each person can only bring one small bag in to the stadium, and it must not be bigger than A4 size: - Height - 297mm (11.7 inches) - Width - 210mm (8.27 inches) - Depth - 210mm (8.27 inches) Bags that are half-full and folded over to reduce their size will not be accepted. Anyone carrying bags that do not meet the criteria above will not be allowed in to the stadium." ;
