<https://planorama.example.org/resource/event/1AdfZ_kGkwvNsnP>	rdf:type	ns2:Event ;
	ns4:sourceId	"1AdfZ_kGkwvNsnP" ;
	ns2:description	"London Handball Allstars Game brings together the past, present and future of the sport for one unforgettable day at the Copper Box Arena. Before the main event, young players will take part in an exclusive kids handball training session, working with handball legends and active players, and learning directly from some of the biggest names in the game. After the training session, the spotlight turns to the court as handball icons face off in a thrilling All-Star Showmatch, playing two fast-paced 30-minute halves packed with goals, skill and entertainment. Expect spectacular finishes, crowd interaction and a celebration of everything that makes handball special. A must-see event for handball fans, families and the wider London sports audience." ;
