ns3:Z698xZC2Z16v-0ZEjt	rdf:type	ns2:Event ;
	ns4:sourceId	"Z698xZC2Z16v-0ZEjt" ;
	ns2:description	"Your box seat in the Ticketmaster Suite includes the following services: * Access to the luxurious Ticketmaster Entertainment Suite 346 with a perfect view * High seating comfort: leather armchairs on the balcony or bar seats at the counter * Premium parking pass with direct access to the Uber Arena (1 parking ticket per 2 tickets) * Separate premium entrance on the west side of the Uber Arena *Open bar including wine, beer, softdrinks & coffee *incl. Beef or veggie burger doors / suite: approx. 2 hours before the show \"Children under the age of 6 are not admitted to the event. \" Children and young people from the age of 6 and under the age of 16 are only admitted if accompanied by a parent or legal guardian (at least 18 years old). Delivery information: *You will receive another PDF ticket via E-Mail approx. 3 days before the event from AXS * Your parking ticket will be sent to you separately as an eTicket a few days before the event by email. * If you have any questions, please contact vip@ticketmaster.de." ;
	ns2:image	<https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/a/6bd/c02199ad-8d22-4668-8973-f400d85826bd_TABLET_LANDSCAPE_16_9.jpg> ;
	ns2:startDate	"2027-02-21T19:00:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ;
