	ns2:description	"Please note \u2022 Mobile tickets are available for the concert. Ticket will be accessed via the Ticketmaster app (mobile tickets). The merchandise will be handed out on site. Shipping if is not possible if not picked up on sire \u2022 The ticket can be transfered up to 4 days before the show. After the deadline, a transfer is no longer possible. \u2022 Information on VIP registration will be sent to you approximately 2 days before the event to the emailadress listed in your customer account. If you have not received an email from this point on, please contact our VIP customer service. Some VIP packages may start before official entry. Therefore, plan enough time for your visit in the early afternoon. \u2022 VIP organizer: Live Nation GmbH \u2022 If you have any inquiries, please contact us under vip@ticketmaster.de" ;
