	ns4:sourceId	"Z698xZC2Z1kuIAYGI" ;
	ns2:description	"Support: Alex Sampson Presented by Live Nation Visitors under the age of 16 may only enter if accompanied by a parent, guardian or person with parental authority (at least 18 years old). No admission under the age of 6! Wheelchair users and handicapped persons who require a companion please call +49 (0)30 - 40 818 824 (local rate). Our competent colleagues from the call centre will help you every day from 10 am - 6 pm. Freya Skye has partnered with PLUS1 so that \u20AC1 per ticket goes towards supporting organizations working to make mental health care more accessible for young people." ;
