	ns2:description	"This is a Mobile Only show. Resale for this event has not been turned on by the Event Organizer. The Comfort Seat tickets include: - Exclusive entry to the Ziggo Dome - skip the queues - Comfort Seat on the Ziggo Dome's VIP boulevard to watch the show* - Free and secure cloakroom - Welcome drink upon arrival - Access to the after-show drinks in one of the lounges on the VIP boulevard * The Comfort Seats are located in the top rows of the first tier. Check the Ziggo Dome website for show times. The Comfort Seats are subject to the 'General Terms and Conditions' and the 'General Terms and Conditions for Day Memberships'. These can be found on the Ziggo Dome website under 'Terms and Conditions' (www.ziggodome.nl/voorwaarden)." ;
