ns3:Z698xZbpZ1k3_b8_d	rdf:type	ns2:Event ;
	ns4:sourceId	"Z698xZbpZ1k3_b8_d" ;
	ns2:description	"VIP TICKETS VIP tickets include general admission to the show. See under 'I' for the contents of the VIP package. VIP/M&G tickets are offered at the initiative of the artist. Melkweg is not involved in the composition and content of these packages. CHECK TIME SCHEDULE AT www.melkweg.nl Access to this event works entirely via your smartphone. You can find your tickets in the Ticketmaster app and your online account. Because the barcode constantly updates, a screenshot or photo of the barcode will not work for entry. For easy access, you can add your tickets to your phone's wallet so you can simply tap them at the entrance. If you want to give your tickets to someone else or resell them safely, please use the official 'transfer' and 'resale' features in your Ticketmaster account to ensure the recipient receives a valid ticket with a new barcode." ;
