ns3:Z698xZbpZ16vkoO4Gx	rdf:type	ns2:Event ;
	ns4:sourceId	"Z698xZbpZ16vkoO4Gx" ;
	ns2:description	"This is a Mobile Only show. Resale for this event has not been turned on by the Event Organizer. Welcome to the Vinyl Room The Vinyl Room is the exclusive listening bar in the Ziggo Dome, where the perfect ambiance and music create pure magic. Escape the hustle and bustle of the main hall and start your concert evening in an intimate setting. Here, warm vinyl sounds, surprising cocktails, fine bites, and atmospheric design blend into an experience you won't find anywhere else. One Vinyl Room Package includes: - Exclusive entry to the Ziggo Dome - skip the queues - Early access - enter one hour before doors open (not to the main area) - Pre & post show toegang tot de exclusieve Vinyl Room - Welcome drink - A warm and stylishly decorated space - Fine bites - Comfort Seat on the Ziggo Dome's VIP boulevard to watch the show* - Free and secure cloakroom - After-show drinks, including bites - Drinks (beer/wine/soft drinks) included** * The Comfort Seats are located in the top rows of the first tier. ** Not during show, only before and after show. Check the Ziggo Dome website for show times. The Vinyl Room Package tickets are subject to the 'General Terms and Conditions' and the 'General Terms and Conditions for Day Memberships'. These can be found on the Ziggo Dome website under 'Terms and Conditions' (www.ziggodome.nl/voorwaarden)." ;
	ns2:image	<https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/a/000/4a939414-8fc8-4390-b5a0-6a8e956b2000_TABLET_LANDSCAPE_LARGE_16_9.jpg> ;
	ns2:startDate	"2026-11-09T19:01:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ;
