ns3:Z698xZbpZ16vvVPajw	rdf:type	ns2:Event ;
	ns4:sourceId	"Z698xZbpZ16vvVPajw" ;
	ns2:description	"The Vinyl Room Upgrade includes: Please note: to benefit from this upgrade, you must have a valid concert ticket. - Exclusive entry to the Ziggo Dome - skip the queues - Early access - enter one hour before doors open (no early access to main area) - Pre & post show access to the exclusive Vinyl Room - Welcome drink - A warm and stylishly decorated space - Free and secure cloakroom - After-show drinks - Drinks (beer/wine/soft drinks) included before and after show, not during the show Check the Ziggo Dome website for show times. The Vinyl Room Upgrade tickets are subject to the 'General Terms and Conditions' and the 'General Terms and Conditions for Day Memberships'. These can be found on the Ziggo Dome website under 'Terms and Conditions' (www.ziggodome.nl/voorwaarden)." ;
	ns2:image	<https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/a/cc6/595243e7-15ff-482e-8f02-16722239ccc6_TABLET_LANDSCAPE_LARGE_16_9.jpg> ;
