ns3:Z698xZbpZ1kCdjO7N	rdf:type	ns2:Event ;
	ns4:sourceId	"Z698xZbpZ1kCdjO7N" ;
	ns2:description	"This is a Mobile Only show. Resale for this event has not been turned on by the Event Organizer. Welcome to the Vinyl Room The Vinyl Room is the exclusive listening bar in the Ziggo Dome, where the perfect ambiance and music create pure magic. Escape the crowd for a moment and start your concert evening in an intimate setting. Here, warm vinyl sounds, surprising cocktails, fine dining, and stylish design blend into an experience you won't find anywhere else. One Vinyl Room Package includes: - Exclusive entrance to the Ziggo Dome -- skip the lines - Entry one hour before doors open (no early access to the main area) - Pre & post show access to the exclusive Vinyl Room - Welcome drink - Warm and atmospheric interior - Full dining experience - Comfort Seat on the Ziggo Dome VIP boulevard to watch the show* - Free and secure cloakroom - After-show drinks, including bites - Drinks (beer/wine/soft drinks) included** before and after show, not during show * The Comfort Seats are located in the top rows of the first tier. ** Not during show, only before and after show. Keep an eye on the Ziggo Dome website for show times. The Vinyl Room Package tickets are subject to the 'General Terms and Conditions' and the 'General Terms and Conditions for Day Memberships'. These can be found on the Ziggo Dome website under 'Terms and Conditions' (www.ziggodome.nl/voorwaarden)." ;
	ns2:image	<https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/a/cc6/595243e7-15ff-482e-8f02-16722239ccc6_TABLET_LANDSCAPE_LARGE_16_9.jpg> ;
	ns2:startDate	"2026-07-06T18:01:00Z"^^xsd:dateTime ;
	ns2:url	<https://www.ticketmaster.nl/event/ludovico-einaudi-%7C-vinyl-room-package-tickets/383720123?language=en-us> ;
	ns4:hasCategory	ns6:miscellaneous-community-civic-community-civic ;
	ns2:name	"Ludovico Einaudi | Vinyl Room Package" ;
	ns2:location	ns7:Z598xZbpZAaa7 ;
	ns2:performer	"Vinyl Room Access" ,
		"Ludovico Einaudi" ,
		"Ziggo Dome Premium" ;
	ns2:organizer	"Ziggo Dome" .
