	ns2:description	"\u00A31 from each ticket sale will be donated to CALM, which is included within the facility fee. Charity number 1110621 Ticket Re-Sale Restrictions 1. Your ticket is a personal, revocable license and remains the property of the promoters, who may request its surrender at any time. 2. Tickets are sold directly to you, the consumer. Any business or trader purchases in violation of terms will be cancelled. By accepting these terms, you confirm you are a consumer. 3. Tickets IMMEDIATELY BECOME INVALID if resold OR OFFERED FOR SALE, except through the Artist's official resale channels or authorized fan-to-fan exchanges. Resale via third parties or unauthorized outlets, including auction sites, is not valid. 4. A maximum of 8 tickets per person allowed. 5. Only tickets purchased through approved agents are valid for admission. The venue reserves the right to refuse entry." ;
