ns7:KovZ91775af	rdf:type	ns2:Place ;
	ns4:accessibilityNote	"Booking Tickets - Please get in touch with us via events@hackney.church before you purchase your tickets with your accessibility and Essential Companion requirements so we can provide assistance accordingly. If you would like to sit in our Ground Floor Access Area please purchase Ground Floor Accessibility Tickets via Ticketmaster. Companion Tickets - We provide Essential Companion tickets free of charge (1 per person) for Ground Floor Accessibility ticket holders. If you would like to bring an Essential Companion please contact us with proof of one of the following documents: - Front page of DLA / PIP / Attendance Allowance letter - Certificate of Visual Impairment - Recognised Assistance Dog ID card - CredAbility Access Card (www.accesscard.org.uk) We are unable to provide Essential Companion tickets for customers who have purchased Ground Floor Standing or Balcony Unreserved Seating tickets. Ground Floor Access Area - Our Ground Floor Access Area is a seated area by the front of the stage with quick access to a disabled toilet. We can also offer table service if you are unable to get to bar during the show. Wheelchair Spaces - Wheelchairs spaces are available in our Ground Floor Access Area. When you have purchased your Ground Floor Accessibility ticket please get in touch with via events@hackney.church so we can reserve you a place. Guide and assistance dogs - You are welcome to bring your guide or assistance dog to our events. Please let the us know in advance. Your visit - If you need assistance please let us know in advance and we can arrange on of our house staff to help you. We recommend arriving 10 minutes before doors open to allow an easier entry. Please note we do not have lifts to the Balcony so if you cannot use stairs and would like a seat please purchase a Ground Floor Accessibility ticket." ;
	ns4:hasAccessibleSeating	"true"^^xsd:boolean ;
	ns4:sourceId	"KovZ91775af" ;
	ns2:address	ns83:address ;
	ns2:geo	ns83:geo ;
	ns2:url	<https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/hackney-church-tickets-london/venue/256341> ;
	ns2:name	"Hackney Church " .
