	ns4:sourceId	"1AgZk39Gkem6wMX" ;
	ns2:description	"A limited number of chair tickets are available and must be pre-booked via Ticketmaster. Two chair ticket options are available: - a chair upgrade for customers who already hold a valid event ticket, and - a ticket plus chair access option for new purchasers. Each chair ticket holder may bring one (1) folding or camping chair, or folding stool. Chairs are not provided on site and must be brought by the customer. Chairs may be used only in the clearly marked designated chair area within the arena. Customers who do not bring a permitted chair will be refused entry to the seated area. For safety reasons, any other type of seating may be refused entry, including inflatable furniture, floor seating, picnic blankets, and non-folding or oversized chairs." ;
