ns3:G5dzZ_GNe-0WD	rdf:type	ns2:Event ;
	ns4:sourceId	"G5dzZ_GNe-0WD" ;
	ns2:description	"No Bags Security measures are in place with bag checks on arrival. Only one small bag per person is permitted and it must not be bigger than A4 size. Large bags - including rucksacks - are not allowed. If you're coming to the show with bags bigger than A4, pre-book and drop them off with our partner Stasher before the show, find out more and book here. To help us provide the best support, please ensure you purchase the appropriate accessible and companion tickets through Ticketmaster at the time of booking. Due to exceptional demand, we cannot guarantee alternative access arrangements on the night if an incorrect ticket type has been purchased. Please note that for the safety of all customers, wheelchairs and mobility scooters are only permitted on the accessible platform and are not allowed in the general admission standing area. Please contact access@o2academybrixton.co.uk or visit https://www.academymusicgroup.com/o2academybrixton/accessibility for guidance." ;
