ns3:G5vHZ_FLnVfsS	rdf:type	ns2:Event ;
	ns4:sourceId	"G5vHZ_FLnVfsS" ;
	ns2:description	"Uruguayan musician, composer, and singer Jorge Drexler - one of the most influential voices in contemporary Ibero-American music - takes to the stage to present his latest album, TARAC\u00C1 (released March 2026). Renowned for a career defined by curiosity, experimentation, and deep poetic sensitivity, Drexler returns with a brand-new live show. Accompanied by a seven-piece band and featuring a completely reimagined stage production, the performance centers on the rhythms of Uruguayan candombe. Fans can expect a repertoire featuring the new sounds of TARAC\u00C1 alongside beloved classics from his extensive discography. TARAC\u00C1 finally belongs to you - join us for this exclusive London show at the iconic Roundhouse to cross the bridges Jorge has built." ;
	ns2:image	<https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/a/8f7/48f298b8-e3fb-4276-ab29-3a2df57998f7_RETINA_LANDSCAPE_16_9.jpg> ;
