	ns4:sourceId	"G5dzZ_1ABR-Cs" ;
	ns2:description	"The international Japanese pop sensation LiSA is launching her first-ever Europe & UK tour later this year. In celebration of the 15th anniversary of her solo debut this year, LiSA will reach fans in Milan, D\u00FCsseldorf, Paris, and London with her iconic voice. This will be the very first time for LiSA to bring her tour to Europe and the UK, and it marks her first headline shows in the four cities." ;
