ns3:G5dzZ_FnXRVP3	rdf:type	ns2:Event ;
	ns4:sourceId	"G5dzZ_FnXRVP3" ;
	ns2:description	"Agnieszka Chyli?ska is one of the most distinctive voices on the Polish music scene, known for her powerful vocals, charismatic stage presence, and bold artistic evolution. She first gained fame as the lead singer of the rock band O.N.A., and later achieved great success as a solo artist, exploring pop and electronic sounds. Her performances are energetic, emotional, and full of authenticity, making her concerts a unique experience for audiences of all ages. Security -- Bag Policy: Large bags including rucksacks are not allowed. There are no facilities to leave large bags or luggage. If you really have to bring a bag -- and it's preferable you don't, please make sure it's small. Only one small bag per person is permitted and it must not be bigger than A4 size. Height: 28.7cm Width: 21cm Depth 15cm" ;
