	ns4:sourceId	"G5dzZ_ulAFEeq" ;
	ns2:description	"Unreserved tickets use fixed tier pricing. Over 8s only. Under 14s to be accompanied at all times by an adult over 18 and sat in Balcony. Under 25s require ID to purchase alcohol. Fixed tier pricing means the Event Organiser is selling ticket in the same category at different prices - lower-priced tickets are released first, and when those sell out, higher-priced tickets will become available. There is no difference between these tickets. If more than one price tier is on sale at the same time - we recommend choosing the lower priced option. A max of 6 tickets per person and per household applies. Tickets in excess of 6 will be cancelled." ;
