ns3:G5vHZ_53I_KE_	rdf:type	ns2:Event ;
	ns4:sourceId	"G5vHZ_53I_KE_" ;
	ns2:description	"Uniting rhythms such as samba, reggae, ax\u00E9, MPB, and dancehall into authentic and irresistible pop, Marina Sena always knew what she was meant for. Launching her solo career, she was propelled into the spotlight by the Latin Grammy nominated phenomenon \"Por Supuesto\", receiving 3 trophies at the Multi-show Awards, including \"Revelation of the Year\". She quickly rose to superstardom in her native Brazil where she now has millions of fans and headlines major festivals and venues. Following her previous sold-out shows, she makes her grand return to London, reaffirming her place as one of the most original voices in current Brazilian music. Brought to you by Jazz Cafe Presents, Como No, and Follow Me." ;
	ns2:image	<https://s1.ticketm.net/dam/a/3e3/99e9210a-0ba8-494d-a115-b96d685db3e3_TABLET_LANDSCAPE_LARGE_16_9.jpg> ;
