	ns4:sourceId	"G5dIZbzpM_abq" ;
	ns2:description	"GRAMMY-nominated and GMA DOVE Award-winning artist FORREST FRANK has announced The Jesus Generation Tour with special guests Tori Kelly, Cory Asbury and The Figs. Presented by TPR and hitting 29 cities across the U.S., The Jesus Generation Tour follows FRANK's completely sold-out Child of God Tour Part 2, this time featuring an in-the-round stage and outdoor venues. Fans will be greeted by the Figs as they arrive, Asbury will lead in worship, and Kelly will open the night by guiding the crowd into FRANK's headlining set. Get ready for a powerful night of music, worship, and community you won't forget!" ;
